OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784076511
OL,3,CRyanair passenger grabbed husband's
OL,4,Clegs as he was sucked through broken
OL,5,Cwindow
OL,7,FA woman who held onto her husband's
OL,8,Flegs after he was partially sucked out
OL,9,Fof a Ryanair plane midflight has said
OL,10,Fshe thought "if we die, we die
OL,11,Ftogether" as soon as the window
OL,12,Fsmashed.
OL,14,FSpeaking to Serbian media outlet Nova,
OL,15,FSvetlana Grkovic said she grabbed her
OL,16,Fhusband Ljubisa Karovic the moment the
OL,17,Fwindow smashed, and held onto his legs
OL,18,Fto stop him from being dragged out of
OL,19,Fthe plane.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
