PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784076511
OL,3,CRyanair passenger grabbed husband's
OL,4,Clegs as he was sucked through broken
OL,5,Cwindow
OL,7,FThe incident happened soon after take
OL,8,Foff on a Boeing 737-800 aircraft which
OL,9,Fdeparted the Greek city of
OL,10,FThessaloniki bound for Memmingen,
OL,11,FGermany.
OL,13,FThe plane was forced to turn around
OL,14,Fand make an emergency landing back in
OL,15,FThessaloniki.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784076511
OL,3,CRyanair passenger grabbed husband's
OL,4,Clegs as he was sucked through broken
OL,5,Cwindow
OL,7,FPassengers reported hearing a
OL,8,Fdeafening bang soon after takeoff,
OL,9,Fwhich Grkovic said was caused by part
OL,10,Fof the engine breaking off and
OL,11,Fsmashing the window next to her
OL,12,Fhusband.
OL,14,FHe was immediately sucked through the
OL,15,Fopening but his wife managed to hold
OL,16,Fonto him.
OL,18,FShe told Nova: "I reacted immediately
OL,19,Fand grabbed his legs. I thought: 'If
OL,20,Fwe die, we die together.' It was
OL,21,Fhorrible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784076511
OL,3,CRyanair passenger grabbed husband's
OL,4,Clegs as he was sucked through broken
OL,5,Cwindow
OL,7,FGrkovic said many people fled to other
OL,8,Fsections of the plane for safety, but
OL,9,Fothers stayed to help the couple.
OL,11,F"Some people came to my aid, I
OL,12,Fremember one man and one woman, that
OL,13,Fman helped me a lot, Ljubisa and me,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"I think he was Albanian, thank you
OL,17,Fvery much. I didn't remember his name,
OL,18,FI don't even know if he told me. I
OL,19,Fwould like to meet him, to thank him
OL,20,Fpersonally again."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
