PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784076511
OL,3,CRyanair passenger grabbed husband's
OL,4,Clegs as he was sucked through broken
OL,5,Cwindow
OL,7,FGrkovic said: "It's important to me
OL,8,Fthat he's alive. He's seriously
OL,9,Finjured and in shock. His hand is
OL,10,Fparticularly badly injured, and he's
OL,11,Fgot burns. He's not able to
OL,12,Fcommunicate, he doesn't remember the
OL,13,Fwhole event."
OL,15,FThe couple had been on holiday in
OL,16,FGreece and were returning home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
