PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784076511
OL,3,CRyanair passenger grabbed husband's
OL,4,Clegs as he was sucked through broken
OL,5,Cwindow
OL,7,FFootage of the aftermath of the
OL,8,Fincident from inside the cabin,
OL,9,Fobtained by Radio Thessaloniki in
OL,10,FGreece, shows the shattered window and
OL,11,Freleased oxygen masks.
OL,13,FRyanair said in a statement after the
OL,14,Fincident: "A Ryanair flight from
OL,15,FThessaloniki to Memmingen on Friday
OL,16,Fmorning (10 July) returned to
OL,17,FThessaloniki shortly after take-off
OL,18,Fwhen a passenger window dislodged
OL,19,Finflight.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
