FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1784076511
OL,3,CRyanair passenger grabbed husband's
OL,4,Clegs as he was sucked through broken
OL,5,Cwindow
OL,7,F"The aircraft landed normally and
OL,8,Fpassengers returned to the terminal.
OL,9,FOne passenger requested and received
OL,10,Fmedical assistance on the ground in
OL,11,FThessaloniki."
OL,13,FRyanair found a replacement aircraft,
OL,14,Fand the other passengers on the plane
OL,15,Fwere able to complete their journey
OL,16,Fthe same day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
